  "3119700": {
    "name": "NOOK FALL：西区",
    "steam_appid": 3119700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/bc3dd64fa800e62a67ccdc8e103341e8.avif?t=1767854828\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到西区小镇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《NOOK FALL：西区》是一款轴测视角视觉小说游戏，我们设定了一个叫【西区】的架空小城，这里即将举办节日庆典活动，在这期间你以一个外来人的身份进入西区，通过十多天的交互和游历过程，逐渐了解西区的现状以及一段发生在三十年前的过往。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/7fae4cacc87cae8e725d34d8f65ef7a6.avif?t=1767854828\" width=616 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经营着一间坐落在城市一隅的安静小店，注视着人来人往，城区喧闹又安静，反反复复，冷冷暖暖，有许多故事就那么自然地发生又结束，假如你碰巧就在这小店之内，也许能收获一些触动和回忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/3fdfa9bed5a49c5d8572f553ddad17c6.poster.avif?t=1767854828\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/3fdfa9bed5a49c5d8572f553ddad17c6.webm?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/3fdfa9bed5a49c5d8572f553ddad17c6.mp4?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c02bdb3849ada6134c160a46a0770b99.poster.avif?t=1767854828\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c02bdb3849ada6134c160a46a0770b99.webm?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c02bdb3849ada6134c160a46a0770b99.mp4?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迎接城市的日落，回到自己另一个温馨的一隅，放上音乐，看报、休息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/9b010d720181fcb7a3c940f2144c7d90.avif?t=1767854828\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras_big/9b010d720181fcb7a3c940f2144c7d90.avif?t=1767854828 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/8de469a4de6e1bdb87ee23a4adcccc21.avif?t=1767854828\" width=616 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以随性地探索这座可爱又富有幻想的精致小城，乘坐电车穿行在各个区域的街头巷尾，不同时间，不同地点都会带来新的感受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c89aab05803c3e9e2d892e4b62efbc3a.poster.avif?t=1767854828\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c89aab05803c3e9e2d892e4b62efbc3a.webm?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c89aab05803c3e9e2d892e4b62efbc3a.mp4?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看似平淡的生活里，短短的西区时光中，或许就将在你的人生回忆中烙下一个独特的印记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c9d653c24382580858b460efeb9c9a3a.poster.avif?t=1767854828\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c9d653c24382580858b460efeb9c9a3a.webm?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c9d653c24382580858b460efeb9c9a3a.mp4?t=1767854828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于制作组</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真理叙志部（NarraTruth Games）是一个位于广州的独立游戏工作室。团队成员有丰富的游戏开发经验和创作经历，致力于在游戏中呈现具有复古美学的艺术风格，以及出色的声音体验和世界设计，进而创作出独特又引人注目的商业独立作品；团队同时乐于创作兼具实验性和趣味的小型游戏。工作室目前正在制作叙事游戏《NOOOKFALL：西区》，预计将于明年继续开发在 BOOOM暴造 广受好评的角色扮演游戏《极东1989》。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于发行商</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GCORES PUBLISHING 是由机核组建的独立游戏发行业务，未来也将不断带给大家 BOOOM暴造 创作活动中的优秀独立游戏。欢迎关注我们的发行商页面。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于BOOOM暴造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机核网旗下的独立游戏品牌。<strong>「BOOOMJAM 游戏创作挑战」</strong>是每年固定举办2次，限时开发三周、限定开发主题的游戏创作活动。在开发阶段结束后，面向所有玩家举办线上试玩游戏节，以及在机核的大型线下电子游戏嘉年华上对这些游戏进行展示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119700/extras/c0ced914650d9748b5ee1ab3db42cc35.webp?t=1767854828\" width=622 height=49 /></span></p>",
